{"tid":1918529,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"保險AA ：「被炒魷魚」","createTime":"2020-03-10T07:11:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T08:48:49.000Z","uid":229185,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1122789552675c79764e4f6fe73a4ae6e8be60c1","tid":1918529,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T07:11:53.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎驟然來襲，香港保險業因中港業務同時收縮而受重挫。業界人士透露，保險公司面談銷售活動幾乎絕迹，內地客業務亦因政府封關陷入「全線停頓」，龐大裁員潮恐如影隨形，估計今年全年整體長期業務保費收入將按年倒退兩成。<br />\n<br />\n為防範疫情擴散，港府關閉部分內地關口並實施隔離措施，市民為降低感染風險亦深居簡出。六福財富管理總經理施維坦言，保險從業員的銷售業務嚴重受累，內地旅客來港投保個案幾乎消失殆盡，直言短期難有復甦機會。他預警，若一個月後情況未見改善，保險公司有機會陸續裁員。<br />\n<br />\n卓越人力資源管理顧問行政總裁梁美儀透露，受社會事件及疫情連環夾擊，部分保險公司已取消員工底薪甚至「炒魷」，若從業員一至兩個月營業額不達標，就有機會被開除。一旦疫情持續，各行各業員工均可能要「大執位」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%AA%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%81%90%E7%88%86%E8%A3%81%E5%93%A1%E6%BD%AE-214500653.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%259A%25AA%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%2581%2590%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%25BD%25AE-214500653.html&d=m5cPLj0qQ3YL0oTVN36eSqT%2B3fxaX50J59AF9IhbNpo%3D&h=7320f8d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%AA%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%81%90%E7%88%86%E8%A3%81%E5%93%A1%E6%BD%AE-214500653.html</a>"},{"pid":"1d615a6ab6a4a4180df3a6cc3c33af88d1e87ae6","tid":1918529,"uid":229185,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T07:12:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7EQWqyU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7EQWqyU.jpg&h=9511c05a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LNtEokA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLNtEokA.jpg&h=e227c2ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d09567535ad28870bf01fd3beead641a89f163b2","tid":1918529,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T07:15:01.000Z